Rating: 4.4 Your rating: n/a Total votes: 99

FNF: Think Positive is an official follow-up to last winter's Friday Night Funkin' mod FNF VS Explosive Benson based on Regular Show, with four new songs and covers in stock. Made by richilix (Animator, Programmer), HippoBoi (Composer), bbpanzu (Composer of Kaboom) and Biddle3 (Composer of Phantasm).
